underlying_goal: Improve a research paper by expanding the related work section and optimizing the placement of a key figure.
primary_success: Correctly identified the best placement for the figure in a LaTeX document for readability and followed user feedback to move it, then successfully recompiled the paper.
brief_summary: The user wanted to improve their research paper by moving a figure to a more prominent position after the introduction, adding references to it, and recompiling the LaTeX document successfully.
